Package: kovel
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: A 3D voxel editor
 Kovel is a voxel editor. It allows you to build 3D models in a easy way.
 It reads KVL files and it can export to COLLADA DAE.
 
Package: kovel-cli
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: A 3D voxel editor (command line interface)
 Command line interface for Kovel. It allows you to build scripts and do
 Kovel operations from the command line.
